X = load_wn18()
model = ComplEx(batches_count=10, seed=0, epochs=1, k=20, eta=10, loss=
    'nll', regularizer=None, optimizer='adam', optimizer_params={'lr': 0.01
    }, verbose=True)
model.fit(X['train'])
X_filter = np.concatenate((X['train'], X['valid']))
from ampligraph.evaluation import hits_at_n_score, mrr_score, mr_score
ranks = evaluate_performance(X['test'][::1000], model, X_filter, verbose=
    True, corrupt_side='s,o')
assert mrr_score(ranks) > 0
